com.clarionmedia.infinitum.di

Class AbstractBeanDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.clarionmedia.infinitum.di.AbstractBeanDefinition
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PrototypeBeanDefinition, SingletonBeanDefinition

    public abstract class AbstractBeanDefinition
extends java.lang.Object

    Describes a bean instance, including its name, type, property values, and constructor arguments.

    1.0
    Version:
    1.0 08/04/12
